37:44.250 --> 37:47.417
RIGHT.

37:47.458 --> 37:49.041
YOU'RE RIGHT.

37:49.083 --> 37:51.500
GO.

37:51.542 --> 37:53.542
DON'T STAND HER UP.

37:55.250 --> 37:57.917
MM-HMM.

38:01.834 --> 38:03.250
