HALF THAT GOOD.

38:36.083 --> 38:38.041
THANK YOU...

38:38.083 --> 38:40.500
FOR YOUR ADVICE EARLIER.

38:40.542 --> 38:43.000
YOU'RE WELCOME.

38:47.083 --> 38:49.792
