DIRTY COP KIND OF GUY.

39:33.792 --> 39:35.250
LITTLE BIT.

39:35.291 --> 39:36.542
YEAH.

39:36.583 --> 39:38.375
MM-HMM.

39:38.417 --> 39:40.875
SO ARE WE DATING?

39:40.917 --> 39:43.041
IF...

39:43.083 --> 39:46.542
DIRTY SEX
ON A REGULAR BASIS IS DATING,

39:46.583 --> 39:49.041
THEN, YEAH.

39:49.083 --> 39:51.041
OKAY, GOOD.

39:51.083 --> 39:53.375
DOES THAT MEAN
I GET TO BE ON TOP?

39:53.417 --> 39:54.875
NEVER.

39:54.917 --> 39:58.333
♪♪♪

40:00.917 --> 40:02.417
