HEY.

40:02.458 --> 40:04.041
HI, DELL.

40:04.083 --> 40:05.417
WHAT IS--
OH, HERE.

40:05.458 --> 40:08.417
OH. (laughs)
THANK YOU.

40:08.458 --> 40:10.417
THANKS.
OH, HERE WE GO.

40:10.458 --> 40:13.458
