40:19.083 --> 40:24.291
LOOK, I-I DON'T HAVE IT
ALL TOGETHER, OKAY?

40:24.333 --> 40:26.709
BUT I'M NOT A KID.

40:26.750 --> 40:29.417
I'M A MAN...

40:29.458 --> 40:31.041
WHO LOVES YOU,

40:31.083 --> 40:34.250
WHO'S GOING TO FIGHT
FOR YOU.

40:34.291 --> 40:38.166
♪♪♪

40:43.083 --> 40:45.041
