40:45.083 --> 40:48.500
HEY.
H-HAVE YOU SEEN ADDISON?

40:48.542 --> 40:50.041
I NEED TO...

40:50.083 --> 40:53.291
♪♪♪

40:58.917 --> 41:02.000
♪♪♪

41:06.500 --> 41:10.083
OKAY? I DON'T CARE.

41:10.125 --> 41:12.500
